findings.proposed_fix:
Use a local copy instead of mutating the shared instance:
```csharp
internal byte[] ToSigningBytes()
{
    // Serialize all properties except Signature using a custom converter or
    // create a shallow copy with Signature = null
    var copy = this with { Signature = null }; // if converted to record
    return JsonSerializer.SerializeToUtf8Bytes(copy, SigningOptions);
}
```
Or since SignedData is a class (not record), use a lock or serialize to a JsonDocument and remove the Signature property.
